{"words":[{"word":"jiuyue","count":5},{"word":"saw","count":3},{"word":"knew","count":3},{"word":"gotten","count":2},{"word":"supplies","count":2},{"word":"heard","count":2},{"word":"settlement","count":2},{"word":"phantoms","count":2},{"word":"people","count":2},{"word":"swear","count":2},{"word":"trying","count":2},{"word":"actually","count":2},{"word":"into","count":2},{"word":"exiles","count":2},{"word":"kind","count":2},{"word":"heart","count":2},{"word":"skills","count":2},{"word":"hehe","count":2},{"word":"research","count":2},{"word":"hmph","count":1},{"word":"bastards","count":1},{"word":"must've","count":1},{"word":"desperate","count":1},{"word":"coming","count":1},{"word":"civilians","count":1},{"word":"nearby","count":1},{"word":"getting","count":1},{"word":"harder","count":1},{"word":"days","count":1},{"word":"tds'","count":1},{"word":"ruthless","count":1},{"word":"close","count":1},{"word":"chase","count":1},{"word":"matter","count":1},{"word":"top","count":1},{"word":"folks'","count":1},{"word":"saying","count":1},{"word":"seeing","count":1},{"word":"lately","count":1},{"word":"sigh","count":1},{"word":"lay","count":1},{"word":"late-night","count":1},{"word":"podcasts","count":1},{"word":"making","count":1},{"word":"eyes","count":1},{"word":"scare","count":1},{"word":"next","count":1},{"word":"paycheck","count":1},{"word":"umm","count":1},{"word":"any","count":1},{"word":"told","count":1},{"word":"must","count":1},{"word":"true","count":1},{"word":"err","count":1},{"word":"luck","count":1},{"word":"find","count":1},{"word":"moment","count":1},{"word":"telling","count":1},{"word":"run","count":1},{"word":"really","count":1},{"word":"mean","count":1},{"word":"fantastic","count":1},{"word":"ha","count":1},{"word":"underneath","count":1},{"word":"generous","count":1},{"word":"beneath","count":1},{"word":"ahem","count":1},{"word":"guess","count":1},{"word":"little","count":1},{"word":"honest","count":1},{"word":"show","count":1},{"word":"gratitude","count":1},{"word":"compliments","count":1},{"word":"small","count":1},{"word":"extra","count":1},{"word":"favor","count":1},{"word":"ask","count":1},{"word":"academy","count":1},{"word":"researcher","count":1},{"word":"everytime","count":1},{"word":"discovers","count":1},{"word":"something","count":1},{"word":"new","count":1},{"word":"running","count":1},{"word":"fog","count":1},{"word":"navigating","count":1},{"word":"mire","count":1},{"word":"already","count":1},{"word":"hard","count":1},{"word":"enough","count":1},{"word":"plus","count":1},{"word":"phantom","count":1},{"word":"incidents","count":1},{"word":"residents","count":1},{"word":"talking","count":1},{"word":"spooky","count":1},{"word":"fest","count":1},{"word":"non-resonator","count":1},{"word":"thing","count":1},{"word":"outpost","count":1},{"word":"short","count":1},{"word":"manpower","count":1},{"word":"guarantee","count":1},{"word":"thinking","count":1},{"word":"lend","count":1},{"word":"hand","count":1},{"word":"assist","count":1},{"word":"figure","count":1},{"word":"speech","count":1},{"word":"witnesses","count":1},{"word":"described","count":1},{"word":"blurry","count":1},{"word":"shapeless","count":1},{"word":"dark","count":1},{"word":"cloud","count":1},{"word":"ghost","count":1},{"word":"dare","count":1},{"word":"risking","count":1},{"word":"worry","count":1},{"word":"rangers","count":1},{"word":"never","count":1},{"word":"goodwill","count":1},{"word":"unpaid","count":1},{"word":"okay","count":1},{"word":"i'll","count":1},{"word":"send","count":1},{"word":"coordinates","count":1},{"word":"general","count":1},{"word":"area","count":1},{"word":"likely","count":1},{"word":"somewhere","count":1},{"word":"near","count":1},{"word":"marshlands","count":1},{"word":"medium-long","count":1},{"word":"hair","count":1},{"word":"pale","count":1},{"word":"complexion","count":1},{"word":"skinny","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Hmph. Bastards must've gotten desperate for coming after our supplies.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"I heard from a few civilians at the nearby settlement that supplies are getting harder to come in these days. The TDs' gotten more ruthless, get too close and they'd chase you down no matter what.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"And on top of all that... some folks' been saying they're seeing phantoms lately...","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"*sigh* You need to lay off on the late-night podcasts...","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"And I'm not making this up. People saw them with their own eyes, I swear!","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"No, no. I wasn't trying to scare you. I just heard from people who actually saw phantoms. I swear on my next paycheck!","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Umm. I didn't see any myself... But those who actually did told me about it, so it must be true, right?","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Err. About Jiuyue... You may be out of luck trying to find him at the moment.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Well, I was on my way of telling you... if we didn't run into those Exiles...","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Do you really mean it? That's fantastic!","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Ha! I just knew it you had a kind heart underneath those skills of yours!","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Hehe, I knew it! I knew I saw a kind and generous heart beneath those skills of yours...","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Ahem, well...","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Well, I guess it was a little too much. But those were honest show of gratitude and compliments!","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"It's just that... I do have a small extra favor to ask. Hehe.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"No, no. It's Jiuyue. You know, him being an Academy researcher and all, everytime he discovers something new, he'd be running off into the fog for more research.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Navigating through the Mire is already hard enough. Plus the \"phantom\" incidents settlement residents have been talking about. It's a spooky fest out there.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"A non-Resonator like Jiuyue off on his own is one thing. With the outpost short on manpower, there's no guarantee that those Exiles won't come at us again...","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"So I was thinking if you could lend us a hand and assist Jiuyue in his research.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"No, not at all. It's just a figure of speech! Witnesses described it as a blurry, shapeless, dark cloud, like a ghost...","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"I wouldn't dare have you go risking yourself.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Don't you worry, us Rangers never let goodwill go unpaid!","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Okay. I'll send you the coordinates of the general area Jiuyue is likely to be in. He should be somewhere near the marshlands. He's got medium-long hair, with a pale complexion, skinny. You'll know it's him once you see him.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002}]}